    "These included top-tier journals (TOSEM, TSE, IST) and conferences (ICSE, ESEC/FSE, ASE, ISSTA, ICST, SAST, QRS), as well as the dedicated LLM4Code workshop.",
    "Finally, we performed backward snowballing on the resulting set of papers, inspecting the reference lists of all identified studies to find any additional research on LLM-based unit test generation that may have been missed during the initial search phases.",
